description= Are you tired of the tedious process of removing old dirty bandages and then applying new ones in Project Zomboid? Do you wish there was an easier way to manage your injuries and stay healthy in the game? Look no further than the "Replace Bandage" mod!

With this mod, you can replace your bandages with just one click, saving you time and hassle. No more clicking to remove the old bandage and then applying a new one - simply hit the "Replace Bandage" button and you're done. This mod streamlines the process of managing injuries in Project Zomboid, making it easier for you to focus on surviving in the dangerous, zombie-infested world of the game.